title: Shaman Active (50)
comment_one: *1= Boost agi to have 405 accuracy (Sand castles) as thats the zone you will be spending quite some time at this level.
comment_two: Put 1 point into active skills, maxing "Power Overwhelming " then putting 40 points each into "Individual insight" and "Knowledge is power" is probably gonna take all your points at this level.
comment_three:
Put 20-30 points into "Virile Vials" (skip this part if you dont have many green vials.)
Go for 1 in each active skill, then you want to max "Earlier Education", after maxing it you can start adding more points to "Crazy Concotions"
notes: This build prioritises farming  Sand Castles as main activity (they should give best active xp/h then)
